    • Constructor Detail

      • Cube

        public Cube(Color[] faces)
        The constructor Cube(Color[] faces) is used to create a new cube with specific colours for its faces. The array specifies the colours in the following order: up, front, right, back, left, and down.
        Parameters:
        Color[] - faces, Array of colors in the sides for which you want the cube

      • Cube

        public Cube(Cube other)
        The constructor Cube(Color[] faces) is used to create a new cube with specific colours for its faces. The array specifies the colours in the following order: up, front, right, back, left, and down.
        Parameters:
        Cube - other, cube containing the sides that you want to deep copy
